docs/deprecated.md
   229Ôćĺ### Short option flag longer than a single character
   231ÔćĺShort option flags like `-ws` were never supported, but the old README did not make this clear. The README now states that short options are a single character.
   232Ôćĺ
   233Ôćĺ- README updated in Commander v3.
   234Ôćĺ- Deprecated from Commander v9.
   235Ôćĺ- Throws an exception in Commander v13. Deprecated and gone!
